cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

The paper proposes a deep learning approach for instance segmentation of fibers in 3D CT scans, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The use of embedding learning also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The merging post-processing method involves graph-based clustering, which could be categorized under computer graphics (cs.GR). Finally, the application of the proposed method to fiber composites suggests a potential fit for multimedia (cs.MM) as well.
